    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im currently on sertraline (zoloft) for my anxiety but the side effects are honestly making me feel so weird and nauseous all the time. i was reading online that st johns wort is basically the same thing but just more natural and without all the chemicals. do u think i could just swap the zoloft out for st johns wort instead? sounds way better to me",
