      "content": "It's essential to understand that abruptly changing medications or dosages without medical supervision can be dangerous. Gradually lowering Zoloft while introducing St. John's Wort could lead to withdrawal symptoms or inadequate treatment of your anxiety. It's crucial to consult your doctor before making any changes, even if it means waiting a bit longer for an appointment. Your health and safety should always come first.",
      "source": "target",
